description:
Positioned in a premium location close to parks and schools, is this beautiful home that has been designed with clever family living in mind. Combined with the beauty and warmth, it simply feels like you have arrived home!

The heart of the home is the delightful kitchen with quality appliances including a dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, stone benchtops and breakfast bar. The air-conditioned open plan dining area leads out through the sliding door to the outdoor alfresco area - perfect for entertaining.

Situated within walking distance to Playgrounds, Parks, Drakes Supermarket, Childcare Centres, and only a few minutes' drive from Westfield Shopping Centre, Ikea, Costco, Schools and various Restaurants - everything is in one suburb right at your fingertips!

Features include:
• Spacious kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, stone benchtops, and quality stainless steel appliances
• Air-conditioned dining area with direct access to the alfresco
• Adjacent living room complete with ceiling fan
• Master suite with ceiling fan, built-in robe and modern ensuite
• Additional 3 bedrooms featuring built-ins and ceiling fans
• Main bathroom complete with shower, separate bath and stone vanity top
• Outdoor alfresco area - perfect for entertaining
• Single lock up garage with internal access
• Situated on a fully fenced 262m2 allotment
• Security screens throughout
• Ceiling fans throughout
• Built in 2011
• Rental Appraisal: $520-$550 per week, unfurnished

Local Schools:
Bounty Boulevard State School
North Lakes State College - Prep to year 12
The Lakes College Private
St Benedict's Catholic Primary School
St Benedict's Catholic College

Short Drive to:
Mango Hill & Dakabin Train Stations
Bunnings & Costco
Ikea & Westfield Shopping Centre
North Lakes Sports Club

Distances:
Brisbane CBD approx 45 min drive
Brisbane Airport approx 25 mins
Sunshine Coast approx 55 min drive

This home won't last long, call Ryan Suhle on 0427 706 699 today and don't miss your chance to call this beautiful home yours!
